      {
        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>Hello {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>I'm back at it after a nice, long bank holiday weekend with the family. There's lots of media news to catch-up on in the coming days, so there might be a few more posts that normal.&nbsp;</p><p>Substack seems to be becoming the new Facebook, in that it's the site we can barely avoid writing about at the moment. So, it seems apt that we kick off with some news that involves both of them‚Ä¶ &nbsp;</p>"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Where Substack leads, Facebook follows",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "koenig-heading",
