          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " ‚Äî to me, it misses some key elements of the story, including the role of VC money in Substack's change in behaviour, but still captures some interesting ideas that I'm still mulling over. It's all about the attention, isn't it? It's ",
            "type": "text",
