            "text": "always",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " all about the attention.  ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "But this sort of petty, vindictive behaviour being played out in public via Twitter is just embarrassing. Even my eldest daughter ‚Äî she's eight ‚Äî knows that this isn't an appropriate or polite way to act. It's no wonder that journalism has a trust problem if this is how some of our biggest names behave. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
