      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Does anyone remember the phrase ‚Äúnew media‚Äù? I do ‚Äî but then, I was a few years into my career when the first newspaper websites started appearing. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I recall being in a meeting in 1996 to talk about our publishers' internet strategy, when one of the senior people in the company came in, and railroaded the whole discussion because he'd just read somewhere that ‚Äúthe ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "intra",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
